rows.label: fev05_210_125_msg0004
rows.name: There must be a lot of pilgrims gathered here.

rows.label: fev05_210_125_msg0005
rows.name:
Precisely correct. Many people arrive
in Acedia with each coming day.

rows.label: fev05_210_125_msg0006
rows.name: And the building you see ahead is the Acedian cathedral.

rows.label: fev05_210_125_msg0007
rows.name: Impressive isn't the half of it.

rows.label: fev05_210_125_msg0008
rows.name:
How 'bout it?
Really makes you feel the Holy See's authority, yeah?

rows.label: fev05_210_125_msg0009
rows.name:
Where do YOU get off sounding
so proud, Shellhead?

rows.label: fev05_210_125_msg0011
rows.name:
Rooms have already been made
ready for you. You'll find them to
the left as you enter the cathedral.

rows.label: fev05_210_125_msg0012
rows.name: We get to stay in big fancy building?!

rows.label: fev05_210_125_msg0013
rows.name:
You are our honored guests here,
after all.
